  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. Substituting 4 for <span class=\"italic\">x</span> in <span class=\"italic\">g</span>(<span class=\"italic\">x</span>) = 5<span class=\"italic\">x</span> + <span class=\"italic\">a</span> gives <span class=\"italic\">g</span>(4) = 5(4) + <span class=\"italic\">a</span>. Since <span class=\"italic\">g</span>(4) = 31, the equation <span class=\"italic\">g</span>(4) = 5(4) + <span class=\"italic\">a</span> simplifies to 31 = 20 + <span class=\"italic\">a</span>. It follows that <span class=\"italic\">a</span> = 11.<p>Choices A, B, and D are incorrect and may result from arithmetic errors.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
